item.title: Need help fixing my dark bow due to silab update
item.dc:creator: @ugetpkd ugetpkd
item.description:
@ugetpkd wrote:

[quote=“nd w0t, post:6, topic:142913”][quote author=ugetpkd link=topic=195633.msg1754199#msg1754199 date=1189720958]

Change the darkbow ID that you have, to the current DarkBow ID… Which is 11785, If that doesn’t work, there is a tut, in Tutorial section by MrQuarter, it explains everything in detail. Do all it says correctly, and you will be able to get the new items.

H2H

I got the new items already whaat was old dark bow id?
[/quote]
It was 7622.[/quote]
I pmd you.[br][size=1]Posted on: September 13, 2007, 11:09:42 AM[/size][hr]I need help making the dark bow as a bow and not a weopon I also need a tut on how to make it shoot dragon arrow’s.
